CAPE TOWN — The body of a 17-year-old girl has been found near a farm in Groot Drakenstein. The grim discovery was made at around 7 pm Monday night. The police's Noloyiso Rwexana said an autopsy would be conducted to determine the young girl's cause of death. "Groot Drakenstein police are investigating a death inquest case after a decomposed body of a 17-year-old girl was found." Meanwhile, in  Ravensmead, a murder probe is under way after the burnt body of a woman was found Tuesday morning. “Police are following up on all leads in order to arrest the suspect or suspects responsible for this murder. Download the Eyewitness News app to your iOS  or Android  device.